{"lemma":"مُشْكِلٌ","slug":"مُشْكِلٌ","root":"ش.ك.ل","root_slug":"ش-ك-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ك-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22863"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B4%D9%92%D9%83%D9%90%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"mixed, made of different assembled contents or parts"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"complex"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"miscellaneous, varied, diverse"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"dubious"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"difficult"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"enigmatic"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"problem"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb أَشْكَلَ (ʔaškala)."},"ipa":["/muʃ.kil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22863","headword_ar":"مُشْكِلٌ","root":"$kl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$okala","text_ar":"اَشْكَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the first of the senses assigned to it above, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Entering among"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confused with"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its likes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And [hence, app., or] accord. to Sh, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ukolapN","text_ar":"شُكْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ redness mixed with whiteness, ” it signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dubious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confused."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Used as a subst.,] it has for its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$okilaAtN","text_ar":"مُشْكِلَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAkilu","text_ar":"مَشَاكِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also: for] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yafuk~u Alma$aAkila","text_ar":"هُوَ يَفُكُّ المَشَاكِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He solves"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affairs, that are dubious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confused."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m$kl","text_ar":"مشكل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$okilN","text_ar":"مُشْكِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], applied to a horse, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having a whiteness in his flanks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dEm","text_ar":"دعم"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D8%B4%D9%83%D9%84/","headword_ar":"مشكل","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23662#8499aa","body_html":"<span>المشكل: هو ما لا ينال المراد منه إلا بتأمل بعد الطلب.<br></span><br>المشكل: هو الداخل في أشكاله، أي في أمثاله وأشباهه، مأخوذ من قولهم: أشكل أي صار ذا شكل، كما يقال: أحرم، إذا دخل في الحرم، وصار ذا حرمة، مثل قوله تعالى: {قَوَارِيرَا مِنْ فِضَّةٍ} أنه أشكل في أواني الجنة لاستحالة اتخاذ القارورة من الفضة، والأشكال هي الفضة والزجاج، فإذا تأملنا علمنا أن تلك الأواني لا تكون من الزجاج ولا من الفضة، بل لها حظٌّ منهما؛ إذ القارورة تستعار للصفاء، والفضة للبياض، فكانت الأواني في صفاء القارورة وبياض الفضة."}]}}